text: “brrda chan chan na thi sædng xohang cak prachachati khxng khea di klaw kæ brrda phu thi thuk nab wa xxnxæ(klaw khux) kæ brrda phu sraththa nı hmu phwk khea klaw a phwk than ru kranan hrux wa thæcring sx læa h nan pen phu thuk sng ma cak phracea khxng khea phwk khea klaw wa thæcring phwk rea pen phu sraththa tx sing thi khea thuk sng hı na sing nan ma”
